name: Suenyo Eco Retreat
address: Jl. Pantai Nyanyi Banjar Kb. No.39, Pandak Gede, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: It's really amazing. It was my dream to stay in bamboo hotel into the Balinese jungle and my dream came true. Suenyo is the place with wonderful and so comfortable bungalows with incredible views of the jungle, especially in the early morning, don't miss this time! But I always thought that bamboo hotels are very hot and stuffy, but the air conditioning works great. A Balinese ceremony awaits you during check-in, which immediately immerses you in the traditions of the island. The breakfast was amazing, all services are really good. I also notice the care in the details when they also bring you an immune shot for breakfast. I had experience of massage treatment in the shala near the river in the rainy weather, it was so atmospheric, calm and really relaxed. You can order floating breakfast and flower bath. Really recommend to enjoy it in the comfort of the jungle. The staff is so hospitality and always help you.
